<br>
Let me jump in with the following suggestions:<br>
<br>
1.  Bill and Jay Gammel's &quot;The Five Essentials of Fly Casting&quot; cost $2.00 from the Federation;<br>
<br>
2.  Mel Krieger's Booklet &quot;Observations on Teaching Flycasting&quot; which is $1.00 fom the Federation;<br>
<br>
3.  Gary Borger's tape on the 15 most common casting faults available from the Federation for about $10.00;<br>
<br>
4.  Bill's tape, &quot;Teaching Yourself to Fly Cast&quot; is a little hard to come by--the ISBN # is 0-9722435-0-X-if you can't find a copy let me know and I will tell you the quickest way to get one.  ( the cost is about $20.00) plus postage;<br>
<br>
5.  I also strongly recommend Mel Kreiger's &quot;The Essentials of Flycasting&quot; which can be obtained from most flyshops and many major bookstores; and<br>
<br>
6.  Mel Kreiger's tape of the same name--you want the first not second version.<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#F9FBFD><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bflyfishingarkansasandmissouri.showUserPublicProfile?gid=chuckeasterling>chuck easterling</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Casting Corner Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 28<br> <font color=#000000>(4/26/03 6:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fflyfishingarkansasandmissourifrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5.topic&index=24>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Certified casting instructor question</span><hr size=1> Hi Jared--<br>
<br>
Sorry, I hit the wrong button and exited before my list was complete.<br>
<br>
7.  Joan Wulff's Fly Casting Techniques, both the book and tape are very good;<br>
<br>
8.  Bruce Richards writes an article on casting the in magazine that is available for free at most flyshops, Fly Fish America, and any thing that Bruce writes is excellent;<br>
<br>
9.  Last but far from least, Tom Jindra writes the casting column for the &quot;Flyfisher&quot;, the magazine from the Federation, and Tom's articles are also very good.<br>
<br>
